---
layout: base.njk
title: "Signal — Early Access"
description: "When Signal is ready, this is where people will find you. Signal profiles surface your real work history for the people who need to find you."
permalink: /early-access/
css: /styles/early-access.css
pageScript: /assets/js/early-access.js
---
<div class="ea-page">
  <div class="ea-content-wrap">

    <h1 class="ea-headline">Start Your Signal</h1>
    <p class="ea-subhead">Signal builds a profile from your <em>actual work history</em>. It's for people who use AI seriously, daily, for real work. Claim your handle to get in, or <a href="/waitlist/" class="ea-waitlist-link">join the waitlist</a> if you're not quite there yet.</p>

    <div class="ea-tabs">
      <button class="ea-tab is-active" data-tab="signals">Recently Joined</button>
      <button class="ea-tab" id="ea-tab-sign-btn" data-tab="sign">Start Your Signal</button>
    </div>

    <div id="ea-tab-sign" style="display:none">
      <div class="ea-top-grid">
        <div>
          <h2 id="ea-form-title" style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 1rem;">Your Signal URL</h2>
          <div id="ea-form-wrap">
            <div id="ea-step-1" class="ea-step">
              <div class="ea-form">
                <input class="ea-input" id="ea-slug" type="text" placeholder="your-handle" autocomplete="off" autocapitalize="none" spellcheck="false">
                <p class="ea-slug-hint" id="ea-slug-hint"></p>
                <input class="ea-input" id="ea-email-1" type="email" placeholder="Email">
                <div class="ea-submit-row">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="ea-next">Next →</button>
                  <span class="ea-hint">We'll email you when it's ready.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="ea-step-2" class="ea-step" style="display:none">
              <form class="ea-form" id="ea-form" autocomplete="off">
                <div class="ea-form-row" style="grid-template-columns: 3fr 7fr">
                  <input class="ea-input" id="ea-name" type="text" placeholder="Name">
                  <input class="ea-input" id="ea-link" type="text" placeholder="LinkedIn or website (optional)">
                </div>
                <textarea class="ea-textarea" id="ea-message" placeholder="What are you working on &mdash; and what brings you here? (optional)" style="min-height:140px"></textarea>
                <div class="ea-submit-row">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="ea-submit">Submit →</button>
                  <button type="button" class="ea-edit-cancel" id="ea-back">Go back</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
            <p class="ea-error" id="ea-error"></p>
          </div>
          <div id="ea-step-3" class="ea-step ea-step-confirm" style="display:none">
            <div id="ea-step-3-pending">
              <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 0.5rem;">We sent a message to <strong id="ea-confirm-email" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);"></strong>. Check your email to confirm your Signal. If it's not there, check spam.</p>
              <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:0.875rem;margin:0 0 2rem;">Once confirmed, you're in.</p>
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="ea-see-guestbook">See Guestbook →</button>
                <button type="button" class="ea-edit-email-btn" id="ea-edit-email">edit email</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="ea-step-3-confirmed" style="display:none">
              <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 2rem;">Your Signal is now part of what's forming here.<br/>We'll be in touch, and feel free to explore.</p>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="ea-see-guestbook-2">See Guestbook →</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="ea-quote">
          <p>&#8220;I built Signal because I was tired of polishing a version of myself instead of doing the work I love. Great work should speak for itself. Let&#8217;s create a better way to get discovered.&#8221;</p>
          <cite>&#8212; <a href="https://erikburns.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Erik Burns</a>, creator of Signal</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="ea-tab-signals">
      <div class="ea-list" id="ea-list">
        <p class="ea-loading">Loading…</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <img src="/assets/images/signal_monkey_bg.png" alt="" class="ea-bg-img" aria-hidden="true">
</div>

{% from "modal.njk" import confirm %}
{{ confirm("Delete your entry? This removes you from the list and releases your claimed URL.", confirmLabel="Delete") }}
